%N A394966 Decimal expansion of log(sqrt(2)+1)/sqrt(3).
%H A394966 H. F. Sandham, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/qmath/3.1.179">Two identities due to Ramanujan</a>, The Quarterly Journal of Mathematics, Vol. 3, No. 1 (1952), pp. 179-182.
%F A394966 Equals A091648 / A002194.
%F A394966 Equals Sum_{k>=0} p(k)/(2*cosh(sqrt(24*k-1)*Pi/3) + 1), where p(k) = A000041(k) is the number of partitions of k (Sandham, 1952).
